node.text: I remember eating this in Taiwan😍

[Tim Ho Wan] - Back by popular demand, Incredible Double is back!
You can now get your 2nd Baked BBQ Pork Buns and/or 2nd Porridge with Salted egg at $2. Limited time only, from now till 1 June.
.
I had the following:
Baked BBQ Pork Buns *promo item*
Special Hong Kong Congee *promo item*
Shrimp Dumplings
Pork & Shrimp Dumplings
Hong Kong Style Egg Tarts
.

Available for delivery on Grabfood, Foodpanda and Deliveroo 
Islandwide delivery on Oddle
I remember eating this in Taiwan😍
